   - The composition `g ∘ f` maps `Additive (𝒪[K]ˣ)` to `Additive (Lˣ)`. The image of this map is the set of elements in `Lˣ` with valuation zero. This is precisely the kernel of the valuation map `v L` restricted to `Lˣ`.
